      "chinese": "石板是魯凱族的傳統建材。自古以來，在沒有好的材料時，魯凱族會巧妙地採用石板。石板有很多用途，魯凱族有八成房屋用石板，人死後也能用上石板。",
      "ab": "ku sahakaikaiyanelringa tudaane ki Ngudradrekai amani kai lrenege. twalai ku nadruma, sakadruwana ku mathahihi ka satwatuma, ngyapapaedhale ku kyalrenege. kai lrenege makalra ku paluludaneini, kai Ngudradrekai lu tudaane yatanulrenege, adrava lu pacai si dralreke miyalri ahakai ku lrenege.",
